template.description: Implementation of dataflow to preprocess data read from a DHT11 sensor, reducing the offload to the cloud.
template.name: dataflow

entry.value: SELECT 'temperature' AS "measure", MIN("timeStamp") AS "start", MAX("timeStamp") AS "end", COUNT(*) AS "readings", AVG(CAST ("value" AS FLOAT)) AS "avg_value", MAX(CAST ("value" AS FLOAT)) AS "max_value", MIN(CAST ("value" AS FLOAT)) AS "min_value" FROM FLOWFILE

SELECT 'humidity' AS "measure", MIN("timeStamp") AS "start", MAX("timeStamp") AS "end", COUNT(*) AS "readings", AVG(CAST ("value" AS FLOAT)) AS "avg_value", MAX(CAST ("value" AS FLOAT)) AS "max_value", MIN(CAST ("value" AS FLOAT)) AS "min_value" FROM FLOWFILE
